    <name>Unit 2 Video</name>
    <intro></intro>
    <introformat>1</introformat>
    <content>&lt;p&gt;For this video, you will need the Unit 2 Handouts located here or on the main course page. These include the &lt;span style="background-color: #ffffff; font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://lincs.ed.gov/sites/default/files/2022-03/unit-2-pause-think.pdf" target="_blank"&gt;Unit 2: Pause and Think Handout&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt; and the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://lincs.ed.gov/sites/default/files/2022-03/unit-2-commun-compet.pdf" target="_blank"&gt;Communicative Competence Handout&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;. For the fillable PDFs, please be sure to save your PDF before closing the document in order to keep your notes.  &lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;Finally, please &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="background-color: #ffffff; font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://lincs.ed.gov/sites/default/files/2022-03/unit2-transcr.pdf" target="_blank"&gt;click here to access the video and visual transcripts.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;After you view this presentation, return to the main course page to complete a short Knowledge Check and the Extended Practice Activity on Analyzing Language and Digital Skills. There, you can also find the Unit References and Recommended Resources. See you in Unit &lt;a&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a&gt;3.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
